  ('elementary-7fec267e-moex-00228', 'elementary-7fec267e', 'elementary-7fec267e-moex-113-b3f42868', 'sub-elementary-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據現行法規，偵查過程中，檢察官在行為人具有再犯危險性時，可先聲請保安處分，成年的精神疾患者 最有可能受到何種保安處分？', '["強制治療", "感化教育", "強制工作", "保護管束"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4177c3d25909", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d775e2e2ff9d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113010", "c": "501", "s": "0102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公民與英文", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7fec267e-moex-00229', 'elementary-7fec267e', 'elementary-7fec267e-moex-113-b3f42868', 'sub-elementary-7fec267e-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '某甲與伴侶乙之親密行為遭乙偷拍並上傳至網路。關於甲之救濟程序，下列何者正確？', '["甲須先經調解無效後方得提出民事訴訟求償", "此侵害行為涉及刑事責任，甲須委任律師提出民事與刑事訴訟", "若乙未成年，其法定代理人同為民事與刑事訴訟之被告", "若甲未成年，須由法定代理人代為提起民事訴訟"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4177c3d25909", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d775e2e2ff9d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113010", "c": "501", "s": "0102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公民與英文", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "一般行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
